@ledger12.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5088

### Login with valid credentials
POST {{ledger12.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "Example-1"
}

###

POST {{ledger12.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout

###

### Whoami (uses cookie from login above automatically)
GET {{ledger12.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/whoami

###

### Login with invalid credentials
POST {{ledger12.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user": "admin",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### Create transaction (Author and Date omitted — defaults to logged-in user and now)
POST {{ledger12.API_HostAddress}}/api/ledger/transaction
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": 99.99,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "category": "Food"
}

###

### Get dashboard — monthly granularity, current year
GET {{ledger12.API_HostAddress}}/api/dashboard?granularity=monthly

###